OL,3,CSon killed mother in her home while
OL,4,Cclaiming 'demons were responsible'
OL,6,FA man who killed his mother in her
OL,7,Fhome, claiming "demons were
OL,8,Fresponsible", has been found guilty of
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,F44-year-old Anna Jones was discovered
OL,12,Fat her home on Station Road in
OL,13,FPetersfield, Hampshire just before 8pm
OL,14,Fon Tuesday 9 May 2023.
OL,16,FHer son Anarlyn Jones, aged 26 and
OL,17,Ffrom Bordon, who was formerly known as
OL,18,FBronwyn Jones but now identifies as
OL,19,Fmale, was arrested at the scene and
OL,20,Fcharged with murder two days later.
