OL,3,CSon killed mother in her home while
OL,4,Cclaiming 'demons were responsible'
OL,6,FDespite this however, the prosecution
OL,7,Fclaimed that Anarlyn had killed his
OL,8,Fmother in a fit of rage after
OL,9,Fconsuming a 'significant amount of
OL,10,Falcohol'.
OL,12,FThe jury heard how neighbours saw
OL,13,FAnarlyn "clambering up the stairs like
OL,14,Fsomething out of a horror
OL,15,Ffilm...covered head to toe in
OL,16,Fred...carrying a bottle of
OL,17,Fbrandy...repeating: 'I've killed her,
OL,18,FI've killed her'".
