OL,3,CSon killed mother in her home while
OL,4,Cclaiming 'demons were responsible'
OL,6,FAnarlyn denied that alcohol and anger
OL,7,Fwere the cause and claimed his mother
OL,8,Fhad begged to be killed due to health
OL,9,Fproblems, but then changed her mind
OL,10,Fduring the attack. However, the court
OL,11,Fheard that Anna Jones had 'struggled
OL,12,Fvigorously' for her life.
OL,14,FHe was found guilty of murder ahead of
OL,15,Fsentencing at Portsmouth Crown Court
OL,16,Fon 31 January.
